How to install the REVERB_2MIX dataset:

1. Install the REVERB Challenge dataset according to the guideline at https://reverb2014.dereverberation.com/download.html. 
2. run CreateREVERB2MIX on matlab interpretor by:

>> WSJ_dir_name = 'path_to_WSJCAM0_dataset_dir';
>> REVERB_dir_name = 'path_to_REVERB_Challenge_dataset_dir';
>> CreateREVERB2MIX(WSJ_dir_name, REVERB_dir_name);

where WSJ_dir_name is path to your WSJCAM0 dataset directory, and REVERB_dir_name is path to your REVERB Challenge dataset directory.

Then, the REVERB_2MIX dataset is created under './REVERB_2MIX/' directory.
